rr,cc = disk((250,250),249)
V[:,:] = 0
V[rr,cc] = Vold[rr,cc]
for i in range(10000):
    V1 = np.roll(V,-1,axis=0)
    V2 = np.roll(V,1,axis=0)
    V3 = np.roll(V,-1,axis=1)
    V4 = np.roll(V,1,axis=1)
    V = (V1+V2+V3+V4)/4
    V[ys1:ys2,xs1:xs2]= Vs
    V[rr1,cc1] = Vc
    Vold = V.copy()
    V[:,:] = 0
    V[rr,cc] = Vold[rr,cc]
    print('Iteration '+str(i).zfill(6), end="\r")
